<AUTHOR>Scott</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>The G8 GT has everything I was looking for in a car - high end looks, great performance, good price, and a domestic make. Fuel mileage is good relative to the performance, but if the first thing you check out on a car are the EPA ratings - this car is not for you. I get great feedback from others on the car and enjoy driving it. My other new car choices were foreign makes but the domestic G8 delivers on all counts.</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>This is my first V8 performance car, and the acceleration is breathtaking. Great, comfortable leather seats. My kids love the full size backseat. Magnetic grey paint choice with the exterior design is very attactive.</FAVORITE>
